                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>Decision maker</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>: investment analyst / asset allocation committee</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>Main decision</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>:</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>Which regional and style-based ETFs should form a balanced international equity portfolio?</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>This project supports the </run>
                <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>full decision process</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>: </run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
                <run fontalignment='0' fontsize='12'>1. Selecting suitable ETFs by different important characteristics</run>
                <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
